            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%B8%95%E9%87%91%E6%A3%AE%E7%97%85%E6%97%A5%23&amp;isnewpage=1" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#世界帕金森病日#</span></a>：早发现，早预防！为自己和家人转发<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[求饶]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fb_a2qiurao-7ad34b9c84.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】不只是老年人，帕金森病是全年龄段都可能发病的疾病。帕金森病的早期诊断率仅26%，许多患者因此错过最佳干预治疗时机。及时识别帕金森病症状，是早期诊断的关键和基础，可避免延误治疗👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%9C%89%E8%BF%998%E7%A7%8D%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%E9%9C%80%E8%AD%A6%E6%83%95%E5%B8%95%E9%87%91%E6%A3%AE%E7%97%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%9C%89%E8%BF%998%E7%A7%8D%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%E9%9C%80%E8%AD%A6%E6%83%95%E5%B8%95%E9%87%91%E6%A3%AE%E7%97%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#有这8种症状需警惕帕金森病#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E6%89%8B%E6%8A%96%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%B8%95%E9%87%91%E6%A3%AE%E7%97%85%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E6%89%8B%E6%8A%96%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%B8%95%E9%87%91%E6%A3%AE%E7%97%85%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#经常手抖就是帕金森病吗#</span></a> （人民日报）<img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hcvqf5hjtmj20mq0ouq9h.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hcvqf5yyu2j20mq0ougrn.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hcvqf6jjwzj20mq0ou44j.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hcvqf6wtlnj20mq0yi12t.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hcvqf7aw8sj20mq0t1wlz.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hcvqf54i7nj20mq0p7q9a.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hcvqf7qzncj20mq0p7afi.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hcvqf853f2j20mq0mu0y5.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hcvqf8mhpxj20mq13048o.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
